videos.description: Jarron Cumberland reaches his hand in to jar the ball loose and hits Jacob Evans on the transition for the dunk.
videos.headline: Cincy converts turnover with two-handed jam

videos.description: William Douglas beats the Cincinnati press with a long inbounds pass to Ben Emelogu II for the dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: SMU long inbounds pass leads to dunk

videos.description: Kyle Washington goes up for a dunk, but he throws it at the rim and the ball still manages to fall.
videos.headline: Bearcats get the definition of a friendly roll

videos.description: Mike Corey and Reid Gettys break down the dominant performance by Cincinnati in a win over SMU.
videos.headline: Cincinnati extends win streak to 16 games
